{"tid":1655541,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[ 葵涌邨召集 ] 10.17 邨內大遊行","createTime":"2019-10-15T06:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T13:44:05.000Z","uid":113441,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"8b041d5fb43b9a23f223ea299f29448f9dde12ec","tid":1655541,"uid":113441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地需要你，一齊反對<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">房署既<br />\n不聞不問</span></span><br />\n<br />\n要求房署出席居民會 交待十月一日事宜<br />\n<br />\n就<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">十月一日</span></span>大量警員入邨以及進行濫捕，令居民人心惶惶，本處於10月3日晚召開緊急居民會，邀請房屋署、商場管理公司「嘉怡」及屋邨管理公司「九源」出席，房屋署拒絕出席。會議上，不少居民提出疑問，但「嘉怡」及「九源」表示需要再向房署查問才能回覆，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">房署的缺席</span></span>，令許多問題不能即時作出澄清。<br />\n<br />\n好多人分別去信要求房署出席第二次居民會，惟房署於居民會當日晚上才明確回覆未能出席。<br />\n<br />\n因此，我地葵涌邨居民發起社區遊行行動向房署遞信，要求房署出席居民會。<br />\n<br />\n行動詳情<br />\n日期：2019年10月17日（四）<br />\n時間：下午五時<br />\n遊行路線：本處集合--&gt;綠葵樓房署--&gt;葵涌商場--&gt;夏葵樓房署<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zWuGfT3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzWuGfT3.jpg&h=a2802674&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"627b4c1c016101377bedccdbdd193a2c55c9e937","tid":1655541,"uid":198590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:13:56.000Z","msg":"等我為大家回憶下決定1020去定唔去<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1655497\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1655497</a>"},{"pid":"fffafe546a71e5ffcd693112acb6734e044817fa","tid":1655541,"uid":113441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:14:17.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e233932cfaf3d43da0c6332c8aba55bc44132cec","tid":1655541,"uid":113441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:14:27.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"e73ef16785c05839e26fb7ec7e99dca86aee5ad4","tid":1655541,"uid":113441,"like